<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Eldrig the Old in Skyfire Mountains has a spawn spot of loc (pos 500, neg 4000). Eldrig is a named Chromodrac, level 51. He summons, dispells (a LOT), melees and cast Boiling Blood DoT, which he will proceed to dispell right away. <br>
<br>
